Size Variations of the App Bars Dynamic Island Component:

| Size | Height (px) | Height (rem) |
| --- | --- | --- |
| S | 40 | 3 |
| M | 60 | 4.5 |
| L | 80 | 6 |

Note: The table above describes 3 possible size variations of the App Bars Dynamic Island component. The actual size variations may vary depending on the specific requirements and style of the app.

In the table above, for each size variation (S, M, L), the height in pixels and rem is described. For example, for the S size variation, the height is 40 pixels, 3 rem. For the M size variation, the height is 60 pixels, 4.5 rem. For the L size variation, the height is 80 pixels, 6 rem.
